Randa El Behery bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri na onye nlereanya.
Nne ya bụ onye na-ahazi ma na-edozi ime ụlọ
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ na Ngalaba Asụsụ Bekee na Akwụkwọ edemede na Mahadum Cairo
Randa wee rụọ ọrụ na mgbasa ozi azụmahịa ruo afọ atọ tupu ọ malite ime ihe nkiri. El Behery sonyere na usoro nke "shames youm Geded(Sun of new day) na 2000
Ọ pụtara na mgbasa ozi na vidiyo.

Ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri telivishọn dị ka Awlad Hetetna (Ụmụ nke agbata obi anyị) na Ga2zat Npvel (Award for Novell), na El lolo2 El Mansor (Pearls Scattered), El Lyl we a5ro (Night and at the End)", na Afaryt el-Sayala (Ghosts of Sayala), Banat Saltandyna (Girl Afan), na El Marsa wewl bahr (Mursi and the Sea), Ahlam Banat We We We Wews and the Public Issue of Laam (The Public Love) (The Public Times) (The Weam)
Ọ pụtara na sitcoms Esht el asfora (Bird's Nest) na Sherif We Nos (Sheriff and Half).
Ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri Ahasys (Feelings) na Aychen El Lahza (Living the Moment) wee pụta na Ayam Saaba (Difficult Days) na Hassan na Marcus.
